## Quality Checklist (run mentally before every edit)

  [ ] Does this change respect module ownership boundaries?
  [ ] Are all values coming from config, not hardcoded?
  [ ] Is every new function typed and documented?
  [ ] Is every exception caught specifically and logged?
  [ ] Are all async functions properly awaited?
  [ ] Does the change break any existing interface contracts?
  [ ] Will this still work if one exchange feed goes down?
